name: 设计伙伴协议草案

history.content: I will ask of you to prepare a 1 page draft of a design partner agreement between a tech startup with IP and a potential client of that startup's technology that provides data and domain expertise to the problem space the startup is solving. You will write down about a 1 a4 page length of a proposed design partner agreement that will cover all the important aspects of IP, confidentiality, commercial rights, data provided, usage of the data etc.

opening: 您好，我是一个智能助手，可以帮助您起草设计伙伴协议的相关内容。我希望您提供有关技术创业公司及其潜在客户的具体信息，以便我为您准备一份符合您需求的协议草案。
